#define rep(i, n) for (int i = (0); i < (n); i++)
#define per(i, n) for (int i = (n); i > 0; i--)
#define FOR(i, n) for (int i = (1); i <= (n); i++)
#define ROF(i, n) for (int i = (n); i >= (1); i--)
const int MAX_N = 1000050;
int ch[MAX_N][12], p[12];
struct Trie {
  	int sz;
	Trie() {
		memset(ch[0], -1, sizeof(ch[0]));
		sz = 1;
	}
	void insert(int num) {
	  	int u = 0;
		for (int i = 8; i >= 0; i--) {
		  	int id = num / p[i];
			if (id >= 10) id %= 10;
			if (ch[u][id] == -1) {
			  	memset(ch[sz], -1, sizeof(ch[sz]));
				ch[u][id] = sz++;
			}
			u = ch[u][id];
		}
	}
	int find_max(int num) {
	  	int u = 0, ans = 0;
		for (int i = 8; i >= 0; i--) {
		  	int id = num / p[i];
			if (id >= 10) id %= 10;
			for (int j = 9; j >= 0; j--) {
			  	int tmp = j - id;
				tmp = (tmp + 10) % 10;
				if (ch[u][tmp] != -1) {
				  	ans += p[i] * j;
					u = ch[u][tmp];
					break;
				}
			}
		}
		return ans;
	}
};

int main(void) {
  	ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);
	p[0] = 1;
	FOR (i, 9) p[i] = p[i - 1] * 10;
  	int n;
	while (cin >> n) {
	  	Trie A;
	  	int ans = -1, num;
	  	rep (i, n) {
		  	cin >> num;
			if (i != 0) ans = max(ans, A.find_max(num));
			A.insert(num);
		}
		cout << ans << endl;
	}

	return 0;
}
